arts.ttl: Ukraine vs France – The French lineup announced without Dembélé
arts.sum: This Friday, the French national team will play Germany in the 2026 World Cup qualifiers at 8:45 p.m. at the Stade de France. Five Paris Saint-Germain players, all French, were involved in the match: Lucas Chevalier, Lucas Hernandez, Désiré Doué, Ousmane Dembélé, and Bradley Barcola. L’Equipe announced on Thursday the likely lineup, with Dembélé likely […]
